<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4704379>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 6. Bayesian phylogenetic tree based on the concatenated cox1, 16S and ITS2 (1580bp). Geographic location for lineages within Clade C [Pimelia (Amblypteraca) chrysomeloides Pallas, 1781] are shown in the map. Support for each node is provided by the posterior probabilities (PP) and ultrafast bootstrap support values (uBS)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4704379/files/figure.png" .

